! Search Enhanced

In-editor search with highlighting and multi-cursor integration.

!! Features

* ''Live search'': Results highlighted as you type
* ''Match highlighting'': All matches shown with visual overlay
* ''Multi-cursor selection'': Select all matches as cursors
* ''Simple UI'': Minimal search bar at editor top

!! Keyboard Shortcuts

|!Key |!Action |
|Ctrl+F |Open search bar |
|Escape |Close search bar |
|Ctrl+Enter |Select all matches as cursors |

!! Search Bar

When open, shows:
* Input field for search query
* Hint text: "Searchâ€¦ (Ctrl+Enter: multi-cursor, Esc: close)"

!! Match Highlighting

All matches are highlighted in the editor with a distinct background color (customizable via CSS variable `--tc-editor-search-hit`).

!! Multi-Cursor Integration

Press `Ctrl+Enter` while search is open to:

# Clear existing secondary cursors
# Place primary cursor at first match
# Add secondary cursors at all other matches
# Close search bar

This enables simultaneous editing of all occurrences.

!! Configuration

|!Tiddler |!Values |!Default |
|`$:/config/Editor/EnableSearchEnhanced` |`yes` / `no` |`yes` |

!! Widget Attribute

```
<$edit-text enableSearchEnhanced="yes"/>
```

!! CSS Variables

```css
:root {
    --tc-editor-search-hit: rgba(255, 210, 80, 0.35);
}
```

!! Notes

* Search is case-insensitive
* Plain text matching (not regex)
* Works together with multi-cursor plugin